summary:
An LLM graduate in Corporate and Commercial Laws from Maastricht University, I am currently working as a Contract Analyst at Medtronic Bakken Research Centre in Maastricht, the Netherlands.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A bit about me:

I  bring enthusiasm and motivation to our team as a Junior Legal professional in the financial services and legal industry. I'm passionate in driving a top tier level of performance to create a unique and satisfied customer experience. I'm skilled in team facilitation, research, corporate and commercial law, and have a sharp attention to detail. I am constantly focused and integrated as the customer’s partner, providing assistance and support in organizational, compliance and legal matters.

Here are some of my skills:

Legal: Client Focused, Researcher, Commercial and Corporate Law, Substantive Law and Legal Procedure 
Soft: Communication, Collaborative, Adaptable, Quick Learner, Analytical, Solutions and Data Driven 
Software: PowerPoint, Word, Excel, MS Teams, Viewpoint (Financial Statements, Legal Documents) 

Language: Italian (Intermediate)
